The APP be submitted to the GPPB on or before the end of January of the budget year and be posted in accordance with E.O. 662, series of 2007, as amended;

At least one (1) observer from a duly recognized private group in a sector or discipline relevant to the procurement at hand, for example, national associations of contractors duly recognized by the Construction Industry Authority of the Philippines (CIAP) be invited in all stages of the procurement to enhance transparency;

 The Approved Bid Documents, Notices of Award and Notices to Proceed and the approved contract of projects awarded be posted in the agency website; 

